00:12:46.766 --> 00:12:49.802
virtualization technology is used by operating systems

00:12:49.802 --> 00:12:52.671
to enhance security by sectioning off parts of the system,

00:12:52.671 --> 00:12:57.676
which is generally considered to be a very good idea, TM.

00:12:57.710 --> 00:12:59.078
